This paper deals with the delineation of Health Service Areas (HSAs) using network-based community detection algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves the analysis of large-scale datasets, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper deals with healthcare services, which could fall under cs.HC (Healthcare) or cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks).
